{"tid":745161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔吼蕭正楠鍾情杜汶澤 唐詩詠愛男生幽默聰明","createTime":"2018-07-16T13:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T14:21:49.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"09920a983e07b8131bf98d38a8e5d5b6700193b8","tid":745161,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】唐詩詠和湯怡出席服裝品牌活動，詩詠表示早前到廣州拍旅遊節目時突然失聲，全程要細聲說話，搞到何廣沛同麥美恩要好留心聽她說話，雖然大家買枇杷膏及藥品給她，吃完也無效，不過完成工作返到香港就無事，有估計她是喉嚨上火太乾涸。<br />\n<br />\n單身的詩詠直認好Dry，問到可有人介紹男生認識？她說：「好呀！可以識到就識，等啲朋友介紹人畀我，交友程式就唔敢，我怕陌生人。暫時只有黃翠如話介紹畀我，講咗兩年，但一個都無，不過她要篩選同過濾先。」詩詠笑言跟翠如要求不要找個似蕭正楠，雖然對方是好男生，但不是她喜歡的類型，更認為田蕊妮老公杜汶澤很好，既有內涵又懂得下廚，她也想識個懂下廚的男生。她說：「我想識個幽默、聰明，不一定有事業的男生，不介意廚師。」（攝影：譚志光）<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xX0RMeGqXw_XRMleIKnWkA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180716f154850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxX0RMeGqXw_XRMleIKnWkA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180716f154850.jpg&h=3b91eeb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%94%E5%90%BC%E8%95%AD%E6%AD%A3%E6%A5%A0%E9%8D%BE%E6%83%85%E6%9D%9C%E6%B1%B6%E6%BE%A4-%E5%94%90%E8%A9%A9%E8%A9%A0%E6%84%9B%E7%94%B7%E7%94%9F%E5%B9%BD%E9%BB%98%E8%81%B0%E6%98%8E-072600512.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2590%25BC%25E8%2595%25AD%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%25A5%25A0%25E9%258D%25BE%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259D%259C%25E6%25B1%25B6%25E6%25BE%25A4-%25E5%2594%2590%25E8%25A9%25A9%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E6%2584%259B%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25B9%25BD%25E9%25BB%2598%25E8%2581%25B0%25E6%2598%258E-072600512.html&d=qqEyEHjbM5O92X0SLE5yGr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=702fa54f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%94%94%E5%90%BC%E8%95%AD%E6%AD%A3%E6%A5